{"tid":2514291,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港電台台灣疫情速報：增8宗確診　明起禁曾往印度人士入境　台居民除外","createTime":"2021-05-03T07:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T08:39:40.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b9849d641a9d7fac6b8e0b3bc0469a2c89e5e58","tid":2514291,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"台灣新增8宗新型肺炎確診個案，其中一名患者屬於諾富特桃園機場飯店群組。<br />\n<br />\n因應印度的疫情急速惡化，當局宣布，明日起禁止14日內到過印度的人士人境，台灣居民可獲豁免，但他們入境後仍要集中檢疫14日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588987-20210503.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588987-20210503.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=7b2660fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588987-20210503.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=713fcec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588987-20210503.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"82605107deb7f173ba3204929f962f243df4e56f","tid":2514291,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:00:00.000Z","msg":"香港；轉機就入得"},{"pid":"3c8f952d8ea90642c11761d694a12a8c29ae6865","tid":2514291,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:32:11.000Z","msg":"台灣都禁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd74292744fc44bc90ae5480862ec6f0b2674760","tid":2514291,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c8f952d8ea90642c11761d694a12a8c29ae6865","tid":2514291,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:32:11.000Z","msg":"台灣都禁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:34:15.000Z","msg":"台灣當局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face